data.title: Meet The Stars of DreamWorks Animation film Penguins of Madagascar #PenguinsMovie – FSM Media
data.text:
Catch exclusive interviews with Rico, Skipper, Kawolski, Private and Classified, stars of the upcoming DreamWorks Animation film Penguins of Madagascar on DreamWorksTV, a family-friendly YouTube channel featuring original live-action and animated shorts along with sneak peeks and trailers to the latest DreamWorks Animations films.

Meet the most entertainingly mysterious birds in the global espionage game as they begin to reveal the untold story of how four ordinary penguins became the Penguins of Madagascar:

Meet Rico

Meet Skipper

Meet Kowalski

Meet Private

Meet Classified

And of course DreamWorksTV wants fans to meet the cast behind the characters – watch as voice actors Benedict Cumberbatch, John Malkovich and more, show off their pre-recording warmups here:

Check out this video if you like conspiracy theories, to see what’s stirring up the around the penguins cast:

For more Penguins of Madagascar, catch them on the DreamWorksTV channel here and in theaters November 26, 2014!
